{"type": "article", "id": 52310, "title": "DVF 任命新总裁，以及，Nike 用 3D 打印技术做了双鞋 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-04-19T02:47:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29397, "name": "安室奈美惠"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 3592, "name": "The North Face"}, {"id": 49478, "name": "V&A博物馆"}, {"id": 1686, "name": "Marc Jacobs"}, {"id": 49479, "name": "Diane von Furstenberg"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180419081414XKsVFTeEDnRzrmbc.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/diane-von-furstenberg-taps-sandra-campos-as-ceo-1202654257/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Diane von Furstenberg 任命新总裁</strong></a> | 周三，Sandra Campos 正式确认加入 Diane von Furstenberg 担任品牌 CEO。在此之前，Campos 曾担任 Global Brands Group 的女装总监，负责管理 Juicy Couture, Bebe, BCBG, Herve Leger 和 Tretorn 等多个品牌。 </p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/exclusive-john-targon-out-at-marc-jacobs-1202654899/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>上任仅两个半月，John Targon 离开 Marc Jacobs</strong></a> | 据女装日报消息，Marc Jacobs 官方宣布 John Targon 将离开品牌。 Baja Eas 的联合创始人兼设计师 John Targon 于今年 2 月被聘为 Marc Jacobs 的低价系列创意总监，其就任时长仅两个半月。目前，品牌发言人拒绝对 John 的离职一事发表评论。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/human-resources/loreal-shareholders-approve-two-new-board-members-1202653487/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>欧莱雅集团董事会来了两名新成员</b></a>&nbsp;| 本周二，欧莱雅集团股东批准两名新成员加入，分别为爱马仕首席执行官 Axel Dumas 和国际运输集团 Thales 董事长兼首席执行官 Patrice Caine。在本次集团年度大会上，官方还更新了与现任执行总裁 Jean-Paul Agon 的任期合同。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>伦敦 V&amp;A 博物馆新展：<a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/londons-victoria-albert-museum-fashioned-from-nature-exhibit-1202654399/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fashioned From Nature</a>。</p><p>展览探索了自 17 世纪初起，时尚和自然间的关系。展出的作品将超过300件，其中包括艾玛·沃特森的 Calvin Klein 连衣裙，它使用回收塑料瓶制成，曾作为绿色地毯挑战赛的一部分参加 2016 年的 Met met Gala。以及 Erdem 绿色花卉连衣裙，还有一款 Christopher Raeburn 的可循环连衣裙。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081811CkuptHiaFJVMSom0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081808POJXEcCweifZtV60.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.627930\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081809LxK32NczJhyRIk0A.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.680664\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081809LSXix3wsbvhnFd5I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.627930\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081809LH29ifME5SqmvVCO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.644531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081809yJZgGo9xPK5QE6eT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081810oYywvgBUKAN6498t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.668945\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Nike 发布使用 3D 打印新技术 Flyprint 制作的全新鞋款，<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/602104\" rel=\"nofollow\">ZOOM VAPORFLY ELITE FLYPRINT。</a><br></p><p>这双鞋将在 4 月 22 日的伦敦马拉松赛事上亮相，由里约奥运会金牌得主 Eliud Kipchoge 穿着，售价 600 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081738IDgkQEUzLfcdGsZX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081744N9mcIytrwjWRfEYd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081748Sh3NEXoD4ruCej5Z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081739AIzg4p6XshO2kED9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081741xb9iFAKOHJNLM2tS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.889167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081827og5RBHbhD7knMOp1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>之前预告过的<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/602018\" rel=\"nofollow\"> H&amp;M 与安室奈美惠的合作款</a>全部公开，将于本月 25 日正式发售，来看看：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081700Zfr4mRhQXDGJYI6O.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.675743\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081703EDl6bTItgJr3Lyxn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.676021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081708XIg3KR7VUuSGycir.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.676021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081708OhwAt2IqGfVdN1vS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.676021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081708zZOAXFrD5bsoQkUS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.675743\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081716EOyawAPNLjedXBIi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.675743\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081716R8OdTrKsxLFnaycX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.675743\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081721UbasEBVAn123h497.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.676021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081722sMWjLXtnhf237dkT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.676021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/the-north-face-launches-new-bottle-source-collection-to-support-national-parks-300631838.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">The North Face 发布 Bottle Source 系列</a>，用回收的废弃塑料瓶子做出柔软的 T 恤和手袋。<br></p><p>该计划目前已经从优美胜地、大雾山国家公园收集了超过 160000 磅的瓶子，<a href=\"https://www.thenorthface.com/bottlesource\" rel=\"nofollow\">The North Face </a>承诺所得收入将捐赠给国家公园基金会，提供给这些公园，用于可持续发展项目。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081646OMsQ5lytge31wxcI.png\" data-ratio=\"0.546875\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081646wrSnMxNKuEY04cm9.png\" data-ratio=\"0.546875\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081646hFDYZg6VpfqtW73o.png\" data-ratio=\"0.546875\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201804190816470RpPbltMFO8qHNgV.png\" data-ratio=\"0.546875\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p>夏天又快来了，潮流网站<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/favorite-summer-slides-buy-guide/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Highsnobiety </a>预测今年的浴室拖鞋风潮还将继续。不妨来看看这些推荐： </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081613Tq6MuX0ovy5xjDiV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081613jY7qH0zQ31P4RukS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081614TwhY1xgEMmkzACl3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081614nWciFxyDhC9orMYV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081613wPDMW48y9rhIQ7Fp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081614ZYWedi2AO4oCRaqN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081614MLADIjQ6d0mizwbf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081614vdOgC6KmYeU7TjIb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419081616yiHraAbNdIcjClfe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：H&amp;M</p>"}